about.summary: Cross-platform alternative to unix patch utility capable to apply unified diffs

name: python-patch
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "patch" %}
{% set version = "1.16" %}
{% set sha256 = "c62073f356cff054c8ac24496f1a3d7cfa137835c31e9af39a9f5292fd75bd9f" %}

package:
  name: python-{{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.zip
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.zip
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install

requirements:
  build:
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - patch

about:
  home: https://github.com/techtonik/python-patch/
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE'
  summary: Cross-platform alternative to unix patch utility capable to apply unified diffs
  dev_url: https://github.com/techtonik/python-patch/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - windelbouwman
    - windelbouwmanbosch
    - abloemert
